headline: Abound Credit Union Invests in Technology Modernization with Jack Henry
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that Abound Credit Union has selected the Symitar® core platform and its complementary cloud-based solutions to modernize the banking experience for its more than 130,000 members across Kentucky.
